short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Boost your customer support efficiency with Brainfish Agent Assist - get instant and accurate answers to customer questions.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Use your customer documentation to get instant answers to questions and reply back to customers across Chrome.
Agent Assist enables customer facing teams to resolve queries and solve problems faster by providing instant, tailored answers to highly specific questions. 
You must be a Brainfish customer to use Agent Assist.
